graph LR
    Operator["llama-stack-k8s-operator"]

    %% External Dependencies (libraries)
    Operator -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime["controller-runtime<br/>v0.22.4"]
    Operator -->|manifest rendering| Kustomize["kustomize/api<br/>v0.21.0"]
    Operator -->|image validation| ContainerRegistry["go-containerregistry<br/>v0.20.7"]

