    Operator -->|deploys & probes<br/>8321/TCP HTTP| LlamaServer["Llama Stack Server<br/>(managed pods)"]

    %% Optional Platform Integration
    Operator -.->|metrics scrape<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS| Prometheus["Prometheus"]
    Operator -.->|external routing<br/>80/TCP HTTP| IngressCtrl["OpenShift Ingress<br/>Controller"]

    %% Configuration Sources
    UserConfig["User ConfigMaps<br/>(userConfig, caBundle)"] -->|config injection| Operator
    OperatorConfig["llama-stack-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap"] -->|feature flags,<br/>image overrides| Operator

